# 🚀 How To Run

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/USERNAME/OptiRoute.git
```

---

## Open Project

Buka folder project menggunakan:

* Visual Studio Code
* atau browser biasa

---

## Run with Live Server

Install extension:

```txt
Live Server
```

Lalu klik:

```txt
Right Click → Open With Live Server
```

---

# 📊 Benchmark Example

| Algorithm           | Distance | Iteration | Time      |
| ------------------- | -------- | --------- | --------- |
| Hill Climbing       | Fast     | Low       | Very Fast |
| Simulated Annealing | Medium   | Medium    | Slow      |
| Genetic Algorithm   | Stable   | High      | Medium    |

